Partnering with Firth Industries for concrete supply provides a very advantageous starting point in achieving your sustainability goals. This is a âcradle-to-gateâ EPD covering modules A1 to A3 from European Standard EN 15804. The declared unit is based on 1m3 of Firth standard ready mixed concrete.
